Incoming messages are sorted within the Message Index under the following categories: All Messages, Loyalty, Fleet, Mission, Resource, Manufacturing, Defense, Conflict, Chat, and Advice.  SD-7 will notify you each time a new message is received; the appropriate icon will also highlight in the Message Alert bar that runs down the right side of the Command Center.  Note that the icons in the Message Alert bar match the tabs in the Message Index; click on the appropriate Message Alert icon to view messages of a specific type. Alternately, click on SD-7 or hit F6 to see All Messages. 